1938;;The Claydon Treasure Mystery;;British;;Manning Haynes;;John Stuart, Garry Marsh, Evelyn Ankers;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Claydon_Treasure_Mystery;;Lady Caroline (Annie Esmond) invites engineer and part-time crime writer Peter Kerrigan (John Stuart) to Marsh Manor to solve a murder. Is the mysterious death of a librarian connected with the Claydon treasure, reputedly hidden on the estate a century earlier?